<div class="modal-header">
  <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
  <h4 class="modal-title">Remove student ({{ student.full_name }} ({{ student.id }})) from course ({{ course.id }})</h4>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
  <p>Are you sure you want to remove the student <strong>{{ student.full_name }}</strong>
    from the course with the course code <strong>{{ course.id }}</strong>?</p>

  <div class="alert alert-warning">
    <h4><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span> Important note</h4>

    <p>
      Removing a student from a course will only delete their final, target and
      predicted grades for the course. It will <strong>not</strong> remove any
      of their criteria assessments or unit grades. These are not attached to
      any course.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p>Please check the details as shown in the table before continuing:</p>

  <table class="table">
    <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Student ID</th>
      <th>Student name</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>

    <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>{{ student.id }}</td>
      <td>{{ student.full_name }}</td>
    </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
  {% autoescape false %}
  {{ form_open({'route': ['admin.courses.students.destroy', course.id, student.id], 'method': 'delete'}) }}
  {{ form_button('Remove student', {'type': 'submit', 'class': 'btn btn-danger'}) }}
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
  {{ form_close() }}
  {% endautoescape %}
</div>